#

Avocado Toast with Cherry Tomatoes

5 min
$3.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

Gluten (if bread is not gluten-free)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganHigh FiberHealthy Fats

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastSnackEasyHealthy

Description

A fresh and satisfying bite packed with healthy fats and vibrant flavors, perfect for a quick breakfast or snack.

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • ripe avocado: 1
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • red pepper flakes: to taste
  • lemon juice: 1 teaspoon
